Text: Nice torrent but not all of these are from Within Temptation. There is other artists mixed in (Lacuna Coil, Cradle Of Filth, Theatre Of Tragedy, etc).

My brother once downloaded all these songs from the official website of Within Temtation. 
They said that all the songs are from the artist Within Temptation. The Composer might be someone else but the artist is still WT.
